summary: After dragonborn defeated alduin, a new threat rose....
descriptionHtml:
My Mods- http://mgmodz-skyrim.webs.com/

This is my first mod so go easy on me-
[youtube] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PjMcui8p_Yg [/youtube]

Description- Vulthurnax, parthurnax`s elder cousin has become the new king of the dragons and dragonborn must stop him

This mod adds a BIG ASS POWERFUL DRAGON great for overpowered or strong people and
there are pygmy dragons flying around his nest they shouldn`t be a problem


so please enjoy this mod, if it is good i will add future updates to it
and please read the readme file for more details


NOTE: I have tropical Skyrim installed, if you are wondering
